HEADWORD: Thomsenolite
<hw>Thom"sen*o*lite</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Named after
<person>Dr. J. <etsep>Thomsen</etsep></person> of
<city>Copenhagen</city>. See <er>-lite</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Min.)</fld>
<def>A fluoride of aluminium, calcium, and sodium occurring with the
cryolite of Greenland.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Thomsen's disease</ent>⟦br⟧
